org.javimmutable.collections.list
Class JImmutableTrieArrayList<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.javimmutable.collections.list.JImmutableTrieArrayList<T>
Type Parameters:
T -
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>, Cursorable<T>, Indexed<T>, Insertable<T>, JImmutableList<T>
Deprecated. use JImmutableArrayList 

@Deprecated
@Immutable
public class JImmutableTrieArrayList<T>
extends Object
implements JImmutableList<T>

JImmutableList implementation using a JImmutableArray to store the values. One possible limitation is that indexes in the array are fixed so if billions of adds and deletes are performed the array can run out of available indexes and overflow.
